(433, '.What is the amount of cement exported from china? Statements: i. China‘s export to America is 65,000 tonnes and this is 8% of the total cement exports 136 ii. China‘s total export tonnes of cement is 15% of the total of 1 million tonnes.', 'Statement I alone is sufficient to answering the problem question.', 'Statement II alone is sufficient to answering the problem question.', 'Both statements put together are sufficient in answering the problem', 'Both the statements even put together are not sufficient in answering the', 'b', 'DATA SUFFICIENCY', '2026-02-27 10:52:35'),
